kkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/104\/categories"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/104\/tags"},{"taxonomy":"post_format","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/104\/post_format"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/meta":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/104\/meta"}]}},{"id":94,"date":"2015-11-02T12:28:21","date_gmt":"2015-11-02T12:28:21","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/?p=94"},"modified":"2015-11-02T12:31:03","modified_gmt":"2015-11-02T12:31:03","slug":"kynningarfundur-2-november-2015","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/2015\/11\/02\/kynningarfundur-2-november-2015\/","title":{"rendered":"Kynningarfundur 2. n\u00f3vember 2015"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"fb-root\"><\/div>\n<p><strong>Hj\u00e1lparsamt\u00f6kin Akkeri standa fyrir <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/events\/1636639853252745\/\">kynningarfundi \u00e1 Loft Hostel<\/a>, Bankastr\u00e6ti 7, m\u00e1nudaginn 2. n\u00f3vember kl. 20.00.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Hj\u00e1lparsamt\u00f6kin Akkeri voru stofnu\u00f0 \u00e1 d\u00f6gunum. Samt\u00f6kin eru vi\u00f0brag\u00f0 vi\u00f0 \u00f3tr\u00falegri bylgju k\u00e6rleika og vitundarvakningar f\u00f3lks \u00e1 \u00cdslandi gagnvart f\u00f3lki \u00e1 fl\u00f3tta.<\/p>\n<p>Markmi\u00f0 samtakanna er a\u00f0 stu\u00f0la a\u00f0 uppl\u00fdsingagj\u00f6f um hj\u00e1lparstarf og st\u00f6\u00f0u fl\u00f3ttaf\u00f3lks \u00ed Evr\u00f3pu og sameina f\u00f3lk sem vill leggja m\u00e1lsta\u00f0num li\u00f0.<\/p>\n<p>\u00c1 fundinum ver\u00f0ur starf samtakanna kynnt n\u00e1nar og \u00de\u00f3runn \u00d3lafsd\u00f3ttir, forma\u00f0ur samtakanna, sem hefur sinnt sj\u00e1lfbo\u00f0ast\u00f6rfum \u00e1 gr\u00edsku eyjunni Lesbos mun mi\u00f0la reynslu sinni. \u00c1 d\u00f6gunum barst ney\u00f0arkall fr\u00e1 sj\u00e1lfbo\u00f0ali\u00f0um vegna skorts \u00e1 sj\u00e1lfbo\u00f0ali\u00f0um \u00e1 eyjunni og \u00fea\u00f0 er von okkar a\u00f0 \u00fearna \u00fati leynist f\u00f3lk sem getur brug\u00f0ist vi\u00f0 \u00fev\u00ed kalli.<\/p>\n<p>Vi\u00f0 hvetjum \u00fev\u00ed s\u00e9rstaklega f\u00f3lk sem hefur \u00e1huga \u00e1 a\u00f0 sinna sj\u00e1lfbo\u00f0ast\u00f6rfum til \u00feess a\u00f0 m\u00e6ta og a\u00f0 sj\u00e1lfs\u00f6g\u00f0u alla \u00fe\u00e1 sem vilja og geta \u00e1 einhvern h\u00e1tt lagt samt\u00f6kunum li\u00f0. Vi\u00f0 getum nefnilega \u00f6ll gert eitthva\u00f0.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hj\u00e1lparsamt\u00f6kin Akkeri standa fyrir kynningarfundi \u00e1 Loft Hostel, Bankastr\u00e6ti 7, m\u00e1nudaginn 2. n\u00f3vember kl. 20.00. Hj\u00e1lparsamt\u00f6kin Akkeri voru stofnu\u00f0 \u00e1 d\u00f6gunum. Samt\u00f6kin eru vi\u00f0brag\u00f0 vi\u00f0 \u00f3tr\u00falegri bylgju k\u00e6rleika og vitundarvakningar f\u00f3lks \u00e1 \u00cdslandi gagnvart f\u00f3lki \u00e1 fl\u00f3tta. Markmi\u00f0 samtakanna er a\u00f0 stu\u00f0la a\u00f0 uppl\u00fdsingagj\u00f6f um hj\u00e1lparstarf og st\u00f6\u00f0u fl\u00f3ttaf\u00f3lks \u00ed Evr\u00f3pu og sameina f\u00f3lk sem [&hellip;]<\/p>\n"},"author":1,"featured_image":95,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"format":"standard","_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/94"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=94"}],"version-history":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/94\/revisions"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/95"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=94"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/94\/categories"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/94\/tags"},{"taxonomy":"post_format","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/94\/post_format"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/meta":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/94\/meta"}]}},{"id":84,"date":"2015-10-28T20:21:13","date_gmt":"2015-10-28T20:21:13","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/?p=84"},"modified":"2015-12-01T22:12:45","modified_gmt":"2015-12-01T22:12:45","slug":"sarah","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/2015\/10\/28\/sarah\/","title":{"rendered":"Sarah"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"fb-root\"><\/div>\n<p>\u00deetta er Sarah, \u00f3tr\u00falega kl\u00e1r, hugr\u00f6kk og fr\u00e1b\u00e6r stelpa sem kom \u00e1valt me\u00f0 blik \u00ed augum haupandi \u00e1 m\u00f3ti m\u00e9r \u00e1 torginu Viktoria \u00ed A\u00feenu. \u00dear safna\u00f0ist fl\u00f3ttaf\u00f3lk fyrir sem kom fr\u00e1 eyjunum, me\u00f0an \u00feeir leitu\u00f0u \u00e1stvina sinna og fundu lei\u00f0ir til a\u00f0 halda \u00e1fram. Fullor\u00f0na f\u00f3lki\u00f0 var oft \u00fereytt og \u00e1hyggjufullt. \u00deau f\u00f6ldu b\u00f6rnin s\u00edn undir \u00feykkum teppum \u00e1 n\u00e6turnar undir sterkum lj\u00f3sum torgsins og vonu\u00f0u a\u00f0 n\u00fdnasistar myndu ekki gera \u00e1ras \u00feessa n\u00f3tt. \u00de\u00f3tt b\u00f6rnin hef\u00f0u l\u00edka \u00e1hyggjur af foreldrum s\u00ednum, gleymdu \u00feau s\u00e9r um stund vi\u00f0 a\u00f0 hlaupa um torgi\u00f0 og fylltu \u00fea\u00f0 af hl\u00e1trask\u00f6llum. Eitt skipti\u00f0 kom \u00e9g me\u00f0 kr\u00edtar. Sarah teikna\u00f0i teikna\u00f0i mynd af fj\u00f6lskyldu og hjarta hli\u00f0 vi\u00f0 hli\u00f0 og vildi vita hvernig or\u00f0i\u00f0 \u00e1st v\u00e6ri skrifa\u00f0. Fa\u00f0ir S\u00f6ru var illa s\u00e6r\u00f0ur \u00e1 sp\u00edtala en h\u00fan haf\u00f0i or\u00f0i\u00f0 vi\u00f0skila vi\u00f0 m\u00f3\u00f0ur s\u00edna og systkini \u00e1 fl\u00f3ttanum. M\u00f3\u00f0ir hennar var fundinn \u00ed \u00de\u00fdskalandi en me\u00f0an fa\u00f0ir hennar l\u00e1 \u00e1 sp\u00edtalanum, var h\u00fan \u00ed umsj\u00e1 annarrar fj\u00f6lskyldu.<\/p>\n<p>\u201e\u00dearftu a\u00f0 fara,\u201c spur\u00f0i Sarah \u00feegar \u00e9g f\u00f3r a\u00f0 taka til f\u00f6ggur m\u00ednar.<\/p>\n<p>\u201eJ\u00e1,\u201c svara\u00f0i \u00e9g, \u201een \u00e9g kem aftur \u00e1 morgun\u201c.<\/p>\n<p>Sorgm\u00e6dd svara\u00f0i h\u00fan: \u201e\u00c9g ver\u00f0 kannski ekki h\u00e9r \u00e1 morgun\u201c.<\/p>\n<p><em>Fr\u00e1s\u00f6gnin er fr\u00e1 \u00c1rd\u00edsi Krist\u00ednu Ingvarsd\u00f3ttur.<\/em><\/p>\n"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00deetta er Sarah, \u00f3tr\u00falega kl\u00e1r, hugr\u00f6kk og fr\u00e1b\u00e6r stelpa sem kom \u00e1valt me\u00f0 blik \u00ed augum haupandi \u00e1 m\u00f3ti m\u00e9r \u00e1 torginu Viktoria \u00ed A\u00feenu. \u00dear safna\u00f0ist fl\u00f3ttaf\u00f3lk fyrir sem kom fr\u00e1 eyjunum, me\u00f0an \u00feeir leitu\u00f0u \u00e1stvina sinna og fundu lei\u00f0ir til a\u00f0 halda \u00e1fram. Fullor\u00f0na f\u00f3lki\u00f0 var oft \u00fereytt og \u00e1hyggjufullt. \u00deau f\u00f6ldu b\u00f6rnin [&hellip;]<\/p>\n"},"author":1,"featured_image":92,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"format":"standard","_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/84"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=84"}],"version-history":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/84\/revisions"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/92"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=84"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/84\/categories"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/84\/tags"},{"taxonomy":"post_format","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/84\/post_format"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/meta":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/84\/meta"}]}},{"id":65,"date":"2015-10-22T20:13:36","date_gmt":"2015-10-22T20:13:36","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/?p=65"},"modified":"2015-12-01T22:12:56","modified_gmt":"2015-12-01T22:12:56","slug":"mona","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/2015\/10\/22\/mona\/","title":{"rendered":"Mona"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"fb-root\"><\/div>\n<p>\u00deetta er Mona. H\u00fan er fr\u00e1 Aleppo og er f\u00e9lagsr\u00e1\u00f0gjafi a\u00f0 mennt. H\u00fan starfa\u00f0i fyrir UNICEF \u00ed S\u00fdrlandi \u00fear til h\u00fan fl\u00fa\u00f0i til Tyrklands fyrir \u00feremur \u00e1rum s\u00ed\u00f0an. H\u00fan vonast til a\u00f0 f\u00e1 br\u00e1\u00f0um n\u00fd t\u00e6kif\u00e6ri til a\u00f0 hj\u00e1lpa nau\u00f0st\u00f6ddum b\u00f6rnum. \u00c9g keyr\u00f0i fram \u00e1 hana og h\u00f3pinn hennar \u00fati vi\u00f0 str\u00f6ndina \u00ed dag. H\u00fan og tv\u00e6r a\u00f0rar konur og tveir litlir drengir deildu \u00feeim fj\u00f3rum pl\u00e1ssum sem \u00e9g gat bo\u00f0i\u00f0 \u00feeim.<\/p>\n<p>\u00deau voru 26 \u00ed b\u00e1tnum. \u00deegar \u00e9g spur\u00f0i hvort um v\u00e6ri a\u00f0 r\u00e6\u00f0a fj\u00f6lskyldu brosti h\u00fan \u00fat <span class=\"text_exposed_show\">a\u00f0 eyrum og sag\u00f0i, \u201enei, ekki bara, en \u00feetta er h\u00f3purinn minn\u201c. \u00c9g skildi um lei\u00f0 a\u00f0 sennilega\u00a0eflir f\u00e1tt tengsl f\u00f3lks meira en l\u00edfsh\u00e6ttuleg fer\u00f0 yfir hafi\u00f0, \u00e1 hriplekum g\u00famm\u00edb\u00e1t \u00e1 fl\u00f3tta undan str\u00ed\u00f0i. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">\u00c9g var vi\u00f0st\u00f6dd \u00feegar Mona og h\u00f3purinn hennar fengu a\u00f0 vita a\u00f0 eina f\u00e6ra lei\u00f0in til Mytilini v\u00e6ri a\u00f0 fara f\u00f3tgangandi 70 km lei\u00f0. \u00deau voru hissa og \u00feeim var auglj\u00f3slega brug\u00f0i\u00f0, spur\u00f0u mig oft og m\u00f6rgum sinnum hvort \u00feetta g\u00e6ti virkilega veri\u00f0 satt. Hvort leigub\u00edll e\u00f0a r\u00fata v\u00e6ri ekki m\u00f6guleiki, og hvort a\u00f0 \u00feau \u00feyrftu virkilega a\u00f0 sofa \u00fati. \u00deau voru innilega \u00feakkl\u00e1t fyrir \u00fe\u00e1 skammarlega litlu hj\u00e1lp sem \u00feeim var veitt, og enn og aftur skamma\u00f0ist \u00e9g m\u00edn ni\u00f0ur \u00ed t\u00e6r fyrir a\u00f0 vera hluti af mannkyninu.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">\u00c9g spur\u00f0i Monu hvort \u00e9g m\u00e6tti deila s\u00f6gunni hennar \u00e1 Facebook, sem var sj\u00e1lfsagt m\u00e1l. \u00deegar \u00e9g svo spur\u00f0i hvort \u00e9g m\u00e6tti taka mynd af henni til a\u00f0 deila me\u00f0 f\u00e6rslunni hl\u00f3 h\u00fan innilegum, dillandi hl\u00e1tri og sag\u00f0i: \u201esvona \u00fatl\u00edtandi? \u00c9g get ekki l\u00e1ti\u00f0 sj\u00e1 mig svona \u00e1 internetinu, \u00e9g synti 6 k\u00edl\u00f3metra \u00ed dag, \u00e9g l\u00edt \u00fat eins og umrenningur.\u201c\u00a0Vi\u00f0 hollenska konan sem t\u00f3k \u00fe\u00e1tt \u00ed samtalinu hv\u00e1\u00f0um og spur\u00f0um hvort h\u00fan hef\u00f0i \u00ed alv\u00f6runni synt yfir. Mona var\u00f0 \u00f6rl\u00edti\u00f0 alvarlegri og sag\u00f0i a\u00f0 b\u00e1turinn hef\u00f0i leki\u00f0 og \u00f6ldur\u00f3ti\u00f0 veri\u00f0 miki\u00f0, svo h\u00fan og fimm karlmenn hafi brug\u00f0i\u00f0 \u00e1 \u00fea\u00f0 r\u00e1\u00f0 a\u00f0 st\u00f6kkva \u00fatbyr\u00f0is og synda me\u00f0 b\u00e1tnum s\u00ed\u00f0ustu k\u00edl\u00f3metrana til a\u00f0 l\u00e9tta hann.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">Og \u00feessu sag\u00f0i h\u00fan fr\u00e1 \u00ed framhj\u00e1hlaupi, \u00e1\u00f0ur en h\u00fan stillti s\u00e9r sk\u00e6lbrosandi upp vi\u00f0 hli\u00f0 m\u00e9r, svo s\u00fa hollenska g\u00e6ti smellt af okkur mynd.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><em>Fr\u00e1s\u00f6gnin birtist upphaflega sem Facebookf\u00e6rsla fr\u00e1 \u00de\u00f3runni \u00d3lafsd\u00f3ttur.<\/em><\/p>\n"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00deetta er Mona. H\u00fan er fr\u00e1 Aleppo og er f\u00e9lagsr\u00e1\u00f0gjafi a\u00f0 mennt. H\u00fan starfa\u00f0i fyrir UNICEF \u00ed S\u00fdrlandi \u00fear til h\u00fan fl\u00fa\u00f0i til Tyrklands fyrir \u00feremur \u00e1rum s\u00ed\u00f0an. H\u00fan vonast til a\u00f0 f\u00e1 br\u00e1\u00f0um n\u00fd t\u00e6kif\u00e6ri til a\u00f0 hj\u00e1lpa nau\u00f0st\u00f6ddum b\u00f6rnum. \u00c9g keyr\u00f0i fram \u00e1 hana og h\u00f3pinn hennar \u00fati vi\u00f0 str\u00f6ndina \u00ed dag. H\u00fan [&hellip;]<\/p>\n"},"author":1,"featured_image":66,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"format":"standard","_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/65"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=65"}],"version-history":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/65\/revisions"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/66"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=65"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/65\/categories"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/65\/tags"},{"taxonomy":"post_format","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/65\/post_format"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/meta":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/65\/meta"}]}},{"id":25,"date":"2015-10-20T23:10:28","date_gmt":"2015-10-20T23:10:28","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/?p=25"},"modified":"2015-12-01T22:13:11","modified_gmt":"2015-12-01T22:13:11","slug":"ani","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/2015\/10\/20\/ani\/","title":{"rendered":"Ani"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"fb-root\"><\/div>\n<p>\u00deetta er Ani.<\/p>\n<p>\u00c1 tveggja vikna langri \u00e6vi sinni hefur h\u00fan veri\u00f0 \u00e1 fl\u00f3tta \u00e1samt foreldrum s\u00ednum, systur og br\u00f3\u00f0ur. Skiptitaskan hennar f\u00e9ll fyrir bor\u00f0 \u00e1 g\u00famm\u00edb\u00e1tnum og \u00feegar fj\u00f6lskyldan rakst \u00e1 sj\u00e1lfbo\u00f0ali\u00f0a sem \u00feau b\u00e1\u00f0u um a\u00f0sto\u00f0 var h\u00fan komin me\u00f0 sv\u00e6sin brunas\u00e1r eftir bleyjuna. H\u00fan og systkini hennar fengu \u00feurr og hrein f\u00f6t, og \u00e1 me\u00f0an d\u00f6nsk hj\u00fakrunarkona a\u00f0sto\u00f0a\u00f0i m\u00f3\u00f0ur hennar vi\u00f0 a\u00f0 hl\u00faa a\u00f0 henni sag\u00f0i pabbi hennar m\u00e9r fr\u00e1 fl\u00f3ttanum.<\/p>\n<p>Arab\u00edskan m\u00edn er takm\u00f6rku\u00f0, en \u00e9g skild<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">i allt sem hann var a\u00f0 segja. Hann t\u00f3k fram s\u00edmann og s\u00fdndi m\u00e9r myndir af drukknu\u00f0um b\u00f6rnum. Hann brotna\u00f0i saman og gr\u00e9t. \u00dear sem vi\u00f0 b\u00e6\u00f0i s\u00e1tum me\u00f0 t\u00e1rin \u00ed augunum s\u00fdndi hann m\u00e9r \u00f6r \u00e1 f\u00e6tinum eftir sprengjubrot. Sag\u00f0i fr\u00e1 l\u00edfinu \u00ed S\u00fdrlandi sem ekkert er eftir af. Mig langa\u00f0i a\u00f0 geta sagt honum a\u00f0 allt yr\u00f0i \u00ed lagi og \u00feeirra bi\u00f0i h\u00fasaskj\u00f3l og \u00f6ryggi r\u00e9tt handan vi\u00f0 horni\u00f0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>R\u00fatub\u00edlast\u00f6\u00f0in \u00ed Molivos hefur veri\u00f0 r\u00fdmd og sj\u00e1lfbo\u00f0ali\u00f0astarfi\u00f0 a\u00f0 mestu legi\u00f0 ni\u00f0ri \u00ed dag vegna \u00feess. \u00cd g\u00e6r komu 3000 manns \u00ed land. Enginn veit n\u00e1kv\u00e6mlega hvert stefnir, en alls sta\u00f0ar er f\u00f3lk \u00e1 vergangi og litla sem enga hj\u00e1lp a\u00f0 f\u00e1. Svangt og \u00fereytt f\u00f3lk me\u00f0 l\u00edtil b\u00f6rn. F\u00f3lk eins og Ani og foreldrar hennar.<\/p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p>K\u00e6ra Evr\u00f3pa, vi\u00f0 h\u00f6fum engan t\u00edma \u00ed skriffinsku og fundah\u00f6ld. Hj\u00e1lpin \u00fearf a\u00f0 berast n\u00fana!<\/p>\n<p><em>Fr\u00e1s\u00f6gnin birtist upphaflega sem Facebookf\u00e6rsla hj\u00e1 \u00de\u00f3runni \u00d3lafsd\u00f3ttur.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00deetta er Ani. \u00c1 tveggja vikna langri \u00e6vi sinni hefur h\u00fan veri\u00f0 \u00e1 fl\u00f3tta \u00e1samt foreldrum s\u00ednum, systur og br\u00f3\u00f0ur. Skiptitaskan hennar f\u00e9ll fyrir bor\u00f0 \u00e1 g\u00famm\u00edb\u00e1tnum og \u00feegar fj\u00f6lskyldan rakst \u00e1 sj\u00e1lfbo\u00f0ali\u00f0a sem \u00feau b\u00e1\u00f0u um a\u00f0sto\u00f0 var h\u00fan komin me\u00f0 sv\u00e6sin brunas\u00e1r eftir bleyjuna. H\u00fan og systkini hennar fengu \u00feurr og hrein f\u00f6t, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n"},"author":1,"featured_image":68,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"format":"standard","_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=25"}],"version-history":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25\/revisions"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/68"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=25"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25\/categories"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25\/tags"},{"taxonomy":"post_format","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25\/post_format"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/meta":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25\/meta"}]}},{"id":19,"date":"2015-10-20T22:41:45","date_gmt":"2015-10-20T22:41:45","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/?p=19"},"modified":"2015-12-01T22:13:19","modified_gmt":"2015-12-01T22:13:19","slug":"eymd-i-himnariki","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/2015\/10\/20\/eymd-i-himnariki\/","title":{"rendered":"Eymd \u00ed himnar\u00edki"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"fb-root\"><\/div>\n<p>H\u00e9r r\u00e1\u00f0a andst\u00e6\u00f0urnar r\u00edkjum. Gle\u00f0ihl\u00e1tur barnanna sem einhver nennir a\u00f0 leika vi\u00f0 og gr\u00e1tur \u00feeirra sv\u00f6ngu og \u00fereyttu \u00f3mar oft \u00ed k\u00f3r.<\/p>\n<p>Vestr\u00e6nir fer\u00f0amenn drukkna \u00ed veisluhla\u00f0bor\u00f0um l\u00faxush\u00f3tela \u00e1 me\u00f0an fl\u00f3ttaf\u00f3lk drukknar \u00e1 hafinu, \u00feessu sama hafi og fer\u00f0af\u00f3lki\u00f0 hefur greitt aukalega fyrir a\u00f0 sj\u00e1 fr\u00e1 h\u00f3telsv\u00edtunni.<\/p>\n<p>En hvort sem vi\u00f0 sitjum og g\u00f3num \u00e1 hafi\u00f0 fr\u00e1 h\u00f3telsv\u00edtunni, e\u00f0a ruggum litlu barni \u00ed svefn \u00e1 gangst\u00e9ttinni sem \u00fea\u00f0 mun sofa \u00e1, \u00fe\u00e1 getum vi\u00f0 \u00f6ll teki\u00f0 andk\u00f6f yfir sama s\u00f3larlaginu.<\/p>\n<p>Og sj\u00e1lf sit \u00e9g og hugsa: \u00f3tr\u00falegt a\u00f0 svona mikil eymd geti veri\u00f0 svona fallega innr\u00f6mmu\u00f0.<\/p>\n<p><em>Fr\u00e1s\u00f6gnin birtist upphaflega sem Facebookf\u00e6rsla hj\u00e1 \u00de\u00f3runni \u00d3lafsd\u00f3ttur.<\/em><\/p>\n"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u00e9r r\u00e1\u00f0a andst\u00e6\u00f0urnar r\u00edkjum. Gle\u00f0ihl\u00e1tur barnanna sem einhver nennir a\u00f0 leika vi\u00f0 og gr\u00e1tur \u00feeirra sv\u00f6ngu og \u00fereyttu \u00f3mar oft \u00ed k\u00f3r. Vestr\u00e6nir fer\u00f0amenn drukkna \u00ed veisluhla\u00f0bor\u00f0um l\u00faxush\u00f3tela \u00e1 me\u00f0an fl\u00f3ttaf\u00f3lk drukknar \u00e1 hafinu, \u00feessu sama hafi og fer\u00f0af\u00f3lki\u00f0 hefur greitt aukalega fyrir a\u00f0 sj\u00e1 fr\u00e1 h\u00f3telsv\u00edtunni. En hvort sem vi\u00f0 sitjum og g\u00f3num \u00e1 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n"},"author":1,"featured_image":58,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"format":"standard","_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=19"}],"version-history":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19\/revisions"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/58"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=19"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19\/categories"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19\/tags"},{"taxonomy":"post_format","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19\/post_format"}],"https:\/\/api.w.org\/meta":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/akkeri.is\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19\/meta"}]}}]
